---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="薬剤師派遣で時給3000円・16時退社｜家庭も収入も諦めない働き方"
  description="残業なしでしっかり稼ぐ。「家庭」も「収入」も「安心」も全部どりできる、薬剤師派遣という新しい働き方をご提案します。時給3,000円以上、16時退社OKの求人を厳選紹介。"
  bodyClass="pb-24 md:pb-0"
>   

    <header class="bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md shadow-sm fixed w-full z-50 top-0 left-0 h-14 md:h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-4 md:px-8 border-b border-gray-100 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 md:gap-4">
            <div class="inline-block select-none">
                <a href="/" class="block hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity">
                    <img src="/assets/images/yakusupo_logo.svg" alt="薬剤師Support.com" class="h-6 md:h-8 w-auto">
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium px-2 py-0.5 rounded flex items-center whitespace-nowrap">
                <i class="fas fa-bell text-gray-400 mr-1.5 text-[10px]"></i>
                <span id="header-date-text">2025年12月更新</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <a href="#register" class="hidden md:inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-full transition shadow-md text-sm shiny-btn">
            <i class="fas fa-search"></i> 求人を見る（無料）
        </a>
    </header>

    <section class="pt-14 md:pt-16 pb-8 md:pb-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-teal-50 via-white to-white relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="relative z-20">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 py-0.5 border-b border-gray-100">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-2 text-[10px] text-gray-400">
                    <span class="border border-gray-300 px-1 rounded-[2px] bg-white text-gray-400 font-medium scale-90">PR</span>
                    <span>本ページはプロモーションが含まれています</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10 px-4">
            <div class="-mx-4 md:mx-0 relative mb-5 overflow-hidden shadow-soft">
                <img src="/assets/images/main.png" alt="派遣にして笑顔で働く女性薬剤師" class="w-full h-auto align-middle object-cover">
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-gray-600 mt-6 mb-8 leading-snug">
                <span class="font-bold">時給3,000円〜 週2日〜OK 残業ゼロ</span><br class="md:hidden"> 子育てママ薬剤師の賢い復職は
                <span class="text-accent font-bold decoration-accent/30 decoration-4">“派遣”</span>でした
            </h1>

            <a href="#register" class="shiny-btn group inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full md:w-auto min-w-[340px] bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white text-xl font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-accent/30 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                無料で求人紹介を受ける
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 px-4 md:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
                今の職場、こんな<span class="text-accent decoration-accent/30 decoration-4">悩み</span>ありませんか？
            </h2>

            <div class="rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200">

                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 md:p-10 pb-12 md:pb-16">

                    <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-gray-600 mb-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
                        正社員・パートの現実…
                    </h3>

                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-auto text-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <div class="relative inline-block rotate-[-2deg]">
                                <img src="/assets/images/full.png" alt="焦る薬剤師" class="w-60 md:w-80 aspect-[4/3] object-cover shadow-lg" loading="lazy">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="w-full flex-grow">
                            <ul class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm space-y-4 border border-gray-100">
                                <li class="flex items-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-times-circle text-red-400 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">子ども発熱で早退のたびに肩身が狭い…</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
                                    <i class="fas fa-times-circle text-red-400 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">「残業できません」が言いづらい空気</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">
                                    <i class="fas fa-times-circle text-red-400 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm md:text-base">社員だと休めない。パートは収入が不安…</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative h-0 z-10">
                    <div class="absolute left-0 right-0 -top-4 flex justify-center">
                        <div class="bg-white text-teal-600 border border-gray-300 rounded-full px-6 py-1.5 font-bold flex items-center gap-2 text-sm md:text-base shadow-sm">
                            <i class="fas fa-arrow-down text-teal-400"></i>派遣なら、こう変わる！
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 md:p-10 pt-12 md:pt-16 border-t border-dashed border-gray-300">

                    <h3 class="text-center font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-8 text-lg md:text-xl">
                        “派遣”という新しい選択肢
                    </h3>

                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-12">
                        <div class="w-full md:w-auto text-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <div class="relative inline-block rotate-[2deg]">
                                <img src="/assets/images/after-haken.png" alt="笑顔の親子" class="w-60 md:w-80 aspect-[4/3] object-cover shadow-lg" loading="lazy">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="w-full flex-grow">
                            <ul class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm space-y-4 border border-yellow-100">
                                <li class="flex items-center">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-500 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base"><span class="text-teal-600 text-lg">週2日〜OK</span>、家庭優先のシフト</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center border-t border-yellow-50 pt-4">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-500 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">時間きっかり終了！<span class="bg-yellow-100 px-1 rounded ml-1 text-yellow-800">残業なし</span></span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="flex items-center border-t border-yellow-50 pt-4">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-teal-500 text-xl mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></i>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm md:text-base">時短でもお金の余裕が生まれる（<span class="text-teal-600 text-lg font-bold">時給3,000円〜</span>）</span>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 md:py-16 px-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 via-white to-white relative">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1/2 bg-gray-50/50 -z-10"></div>
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-gray-500 text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold mb-3 shadow-sm">
                    選ばれる4つの理由
                </span>
                <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 leading-tight">
                    「家庭」も「収入」も「安心」も。<br>
                    <span class="text-primary px-2 rounded mt-2 inline-block">全部どりできる働き方</span>
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden relative pb-4">
                <div class="p-5 md:p-8 pb-2 md:pb-6">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-0 md:gap-8 relative z-10 divide-y divide-gray-100 md:divide-y-0">

                        <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center group py-6 md:py-0">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6 md:mr-0 md:mb-4 text-teal-500 text-4xl md:text-5xl group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-base md:text-lg mb-1 md:mb-2">16時退社OK</h3>
                                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                    <strong class="font-bold text-gray-700">残業なし</strong>契約が可能。<br class="hidden md:inline">
                                    保育園の<strong class="font-bold text-gray-700">お迎え</strong>も余裕です。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center group py-6 md:py-0 md:border-x md:border-gray-50">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6 md:mr-0 md:mb-4 text-yellow-500 text-4xl md:text-5xl group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-yen-sign fa-fw"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-base md:text-lg mb-1 md:mb-2">時給3,000円〜</h3>
                                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                    短時間でも効率よく稼げる。<br class="hidden md:inline">
                                    <strong class="font-bold text-gray-700">高単価求人</strong>が多数。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center md:flex-col md:text-center group py-6 md:py-0">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6 md:mr-0 md:mb-4 text-red-400 text-4xl md:text-5xl group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-300 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-book-reader"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-base md:text-lg mb-1 md:mb-2">ブランク研修</h3>
                                <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                                    <strong class="font-bold text-gray-700">復職支援プログラム</strong>で<br class="hidden md:inline">
                                    知識をアップデート。
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center py-2 md:py-3">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center px-6 md:px-10">
                        <div class="w-full border-t border-dashed border-gray-200"></div>
                    </div>
                    <span class="relative bg-white px-3 text-[10px] text-gray-400 font-bold flex items-center gap-1 z-10">
                        <i class="fas fa-plus-circle text-teal-400"></i> さらに安心の保障
                    </span>
                </div>

                <div class="px-5 md:px-10 py-2 md:py-4">
                    <div class="bg-gray-50/50 rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-100 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-3 md:gap-8">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center md:text-left w-full md:w-auto">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2 mb-2 md:mb-0">
                                <i class="fas fa-shield-cat text-teal-500 text-base md:text-lg"></i>
                                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-700 text-sm">福利厚生も完備</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex-grow w-full">
                            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-2">
                                <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 text-xs mr-2"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-600">社会保険 即日加入</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 text-xs mr-2"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-600">有給消化率 ほぼ100%</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center bg-white px-3 py-2 rounded-lg border border-gray-100 shadow-sm">
                                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-500 text-xs mr-2"></i>
                                    <span class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-600">産休育休・健康診断</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-400 text-center md:text-right mt-2">※加入条件等はご紹介時にご確認ください</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 md:py-16 px-4 bg-teal-50/50 border-teal-100">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8 md:mb-12">
                「働き方を変えてよかった」<br>先輩ママの声
            </h2>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-6 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100">
                    <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                        <img src="/assets/images/user01.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">34歳・子供2人</span>
                        <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">高時給派遣・エリア重視</span>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                            お迎えの焦りから解放。<br>
                            通勤時間が<span class="text-accent">30分短縮!</span>
                        </h3>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                                <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">転職前</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through">通勤45分・残業あり</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                                <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base">通勤15分・残業ゼロ</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                            以前は延長保育に頼り切りでしたが、今は16時に退社。自宅近くのクリニックを紹介してもらい、夕飯を子供と作る余裕が生まれました。
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="more-reviews" class="hidden md:contents">
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100 animate-fade-in">
                        <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                            <img src="/assets/images/user02.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">42歳・扶養内希望</span>
                            <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">高時給派遣</span>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                                働く時間は減ったのに、<br>
                                時給<span class="text-accent">900円UP</span>で収入維持！
                            </h3>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                                    <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">転職前</span>
                                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through">時給 2,200円</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                                    <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base">時給 3,100円</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                                「派遣はハードルが高い」と思っていましたが、担当者の交渉で扶養内調整もスムーズに。短時間で効率よく家計を支えられています。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-6 pt-10 md:p-8 md:pt-12 rounded-2xl shadow-soft relative mt-10 md:mt-0 border border-gray-100 animate-fade-in">
                        <div class="absolute -top-6 md:-top-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
                            <img src="/assets/images/user03.png" alt="User" loading="lazy" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full border-4 border-white shadow-md object-cover" loading="lazy">
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center">
                            <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-gray-500 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">39歳・ブランク3年</span>
                            <span class="inline-block bg-gray-100 text-teal-600 text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded mb-3">リハビリ復帰</span>
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-lg mb-5 leading-snug">
                                新薬知識ゼロから復帰。<br>
                                <span class="text-accent">週3日・1日4時間</span>で再スタート
                            </h3>
                            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4 text-sm">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
                                    <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">不安</span>
                                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium line-through">知識不足・体力</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <span class="text-teal-600 text-xs font-bold">現在</span>
                                    <span class="text-gray-800 font-bold text-base">研修充実・監査メイン</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-sub-text text-left leading-relaxed">
                                いきなりのフルタイムは怖かったので、理解のある店舗を紹介してもらいました。e-learningでの研修制度も使えて、自信を取り戻せました。
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 text-center md:hidden">
                <button id="show-more-btn" onclick="toggleReviews()" class="bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-600 font-bold py-3 px-10 rounded-full shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-50 transition active:scale-95 text-sm flex items-center mx-auto gap-2">
                    <span>他の口コミも見る</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down text-xs"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script is:inline>
        function toggleReviews() {
            const moreReviews = document.getElementById('more-reviews');
            const btn = document.getElementById('show-more-btn');
            moreReviews.classList.remove('hidden');
            btn.style.display = 'none';
        }
    </script>

    <section class="bg-gray-100 py-12 px-4 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold mb-3">例えば、こんな求人があります</h2>
                <p class="text-center text-xs text-sub-text mb-8">※実際の内容は派遣求人先でご確認ください</p>

                <div class="swiper mySwiper px-4">
                    
                    <div class="swiper-wrapper !items-stretch">

                        <div class="swiper-slide !h-auto !flex">
                            <div class="w-full bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-md border-t-4 border-primary relative flex flex-col overflow-hidden h-full">
                                <div class="h-32 bg-gray-200 w-full relative shrink-0">
                                    <img src="/assets/images/ex01.png" alt="職場の雰囲気" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy">
                                    <span class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-accent text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm">週2日でも可能</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow">
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-sub-text">
                                        <span class="bg-gray-100 px-2 py-1 rounded user-area-text">お近くの</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-gray-800 mb-4 leading-snug">ママさん薬剤師活躍中！急なお休みも協力体制あり</h3>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm"><span class="w-12 font-bold text-gray-400 text-xs">時給</span><span class="font-bold text-accent text-lg">3,300円</span></div>
                                        <div class="flex items-center text-sm"><span class="w-12 font-bold text-gray-400 text-xs">時間</span><span class="font-bold text-gray-700">9:00〜15:00</span></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="swiper-slide !h-auto !flex">
